# google-services.json contains Firebase project secrets; never commit the real one.
# Use app/google-services.placeholder.json as a template.
android-app/app/google-services.json
# NOTE: android-app/app/keystore/release.jks IS committed intentionally.
# It is a self-signed key for a private family sideload app (not Play Store).
# Committing it ensures every build (local + CI) produces the same signature,
# so app updates install without requiring an uninstall.

